review.name: Excellent!
review.reviewBody:
This was one of the best shows I have seen in years! These boys have an amazing talent that they are able to share to the world! I especially loved the staging and the effects that they used. The giant clown face kind of scared me though! The lasers, moving stage, and lights were very very good too.

I recommend that everyone goes to see them in concert!
